那那聲上番岸，唔好浪費自己時間，你唔放棄愛佢既念頭你只會愈黎愈辛苦<br />\n<br />\n過來人，寧願自己一個，也不要將心放係個冇結局既故事上"},{"pid":"afae0234f99380f818a8ca23854a2d0a9e1e6f64","tid":390102,"uid":135416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T07:26:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢理返我啦，佢好似無事發生過咁<br />\n咁樣係好定唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n吊緊鹽水<br />\n利申：被飛的過來人"},{"pid":"506874fd8480db13a2fea631a296d4957ac4e0c0","tid":390102,"uid":2059,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T07:26:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我唔想分手，仲係好愛佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以點算</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本官認為<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">帽</span></span>d甘既事！<br />\n放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">甘你老母</span>"},{"pid":"dfde1533ae86f0749b4ad72b6c3db096a16fb5b7","tid":390102,"uid":65726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T09:01:38.000Z","msg":"救個閪咩 各安天命啦"},{"pid":"f01ecba5e1b05f1e7f475a88dc7e9d33a049d290","tid":390102,"uid":50826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T09:02:04.000Z","msg":"買熊"},{"pid":"620e123b62aa360a2c910da165a83557077c5d00","tid":390102,"uid":36334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T09:03:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我唔想分手，仲係好愛佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以點算</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本官認為<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">帽</span></span>d甘既事！<br />\n放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n字都唔撚識打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abd0743259a2ac1f4c270bd498f0497bfe5d5c0b","tid":390102,"uid":50647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T09:10:14.000Z","msg":"淡嘅原因好大機會帽左<i